us – Den Namen Jesu Christi auf uns nehmen</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114239216\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.23-25?lang=deu#p23\">LuB 18:23-25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114239217\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/26.24-27?lang=deu#p24\">Mos 26:24-27</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"15\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note15a\" data-full-marker=\"15a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114239218\" id=\"note15a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/calling-and-election?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Berufung und Erwählung</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/sanctification?lang=deu\">Heiligung</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note15b\" data-full-marker=\"15b\">\n<p data-aid=\"114239219\" id=\"note15b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/col/1.16?lang=deu#p16\">Kol 1:16</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.2?lang=deu#p2\">Mos 4:2</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.39?lang=deu#p39\">Al 11:39</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"p1":[{"id":"video1","refId":"6133144214FB949047874F55D47E29C6D926A3FE","assetId":"6133144214FB949047874F55D47E29C6D926A3FE","duration":"220373","ip":"Download &amp; Streaming","videoId":"6249420006001","videoDescription":"König Benjamins Volk verspürt den Geist des Herrn und schließt mit Gott den Bund, den Namen Christi auf sich zu nehmen und seine Gebote zu halten. Sie werden Kinder Christi genannt, weil sie aus Got